e-jaoe38c1mohao6cs.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mohao6cr/e88e89cd-14b8-4079-947c-acd0d4e583fa/a75a0fb0-4245-11f1-a7dd-e720d6840823/file-jaoe38c1mohao6cs.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 5th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 3 English Explanation 4\"></p>",
